(BranchPredictor, decodeWidth).explanation: Branch predictor accuracy and decode width are independent architectural design parameters that don't directly influence each other;

(BranchPredictor, numRCQEntries).explanation: Branch predictor mechanisms and the number of request completion queue entries are separate architectural components with no direct causal relationship;

(BranchPredictor, flush).explanation: Poor branch prediction accuracy directly causes pipeline flushes when mispredictions occur, requiring the processor to discard incorrectly fetched instructions;
